{"tid":2103071,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【泛民初選】本土派素人聯合造勢 民主黨黃國桐撐新人馮達浚","createTime":"2020-07-11T03:11:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-11T05:12:29.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c941365b7d945f11e9cb4bbce54b55f8d6b307bf","tid":2103071,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T03:11:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200711/YSSVXUV6A254D5W24UL5KUFNTE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200711%2FYSSVXUV6A254D5W24UL5KUFNTE%2F&d=FEUhZFrEoh9TukhHyG%2BZyOoeOpwBOZOods3%2BbOb6780%3D&h=bfa63108\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200711%2FYSSVXUV6A254D5W24UL5KUFNTE%2F&h=760db62e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200711/YSSVXUV6A254D5W24UL5KUFNTE/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n【泛民初選】本土派素人聯合造勢 民主黨黃國桐撐新人馮達浚<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/O9_L8ZHx_h9Dme3WFBou4tm6JaQ=/640x392/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/MMN52J7OZWACUFTIAAZE5HJBPY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FO9_L8ZHx_h9Dme3WFBou4tm6JaQ%3D%2F640x392%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FMMN52J7OZWACUFTIAAZE5HJBPY.jpg&h=c64d8517&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n本報記者攝<br />\n(蘋果日報)<br />\n<br />\n民主派今天（11日）將舉行立法會選舉初選，各候選人趁最後機會造勢，呼籲市民支持。參選九西的「九龍城大小事」主席馮達浚獲民主黨九龍城區議員黃國桐現身支持，馮達浚相信自己與黃國桐政治理念相同，故獲「桐叔」跨黨支持，至於黃國桐則未有接受訪問。<br />\n<br />\n本身為民主黨成員的黃國桐，並無支持同樣參與初選的黨友黃碧雲，<br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n，呼籲選民全票支持馮達浚。<br />\n<br />\n除了傳統泛民，馮亦獲本土派區議員站台。參與超區初選的元朗區議員王百羽呼籲本土派支持者投票予馮達浚，<br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n改變議會生態。"},{"pid":"a6a89dc172f13b7a246d42bf387c3924e0295e53","tid":2103071,"uid":225100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T05:12:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}